TextEng: Speak quickly! What do you want with me?
Text: 빨리 말해! 나한테 원하는 게 뭐야?

TextEng: Speaks quick! What you wants?
Forget it. I'll leave you be.
What are you? How did you get here?
Text: 넌 뭐야? 어떻게 여기 온 거야?

TextEng: I might consider helping you...
What do you mean by your 'brother?' What is this amulet?
What is you? How you gets here?
Me might helps you...
What you means 'brother?' What is amulet?
Why do you need this amulet so badly?
Text: 그 호신부가 왜 그렇게 필요한 거야?

TextEng: Why don't you just get it yourself?
What reward do I get out of this?
Okay, I'll do it.
Why you wants amulet so bad?
Why you not go gets it?
What reward me gets?
Okay, me do it.
I have some more questions about this.
Text: 이것에 대해 질문이 좀 더 있어.

TextEng: I want something up front before I do this.
Text: 이거 하기 전에 뭔가 먼저 받고 싶어.

TextEng: Me got some questions 'bout job.
Me wants something now before me does this.
Text: 이거 하기 전에 뭔가 지금 원해.

TextEng: Why do you need this amulet so badly?
Text: 그 호신부가 왜 그렇게 필요한 거야?

TextEng: Why don't you just get it yourself?
What reward do I get out of this?
Why you wants amulet so bad?
Why don't you just get it yourself?
What reward me gets?
I have a question about getting that amulet.
Text: 그 호신부 가져오는 것에 대해 질문이 있어.

TextEng: Me has question about getting amulet
I have the amulet right here.
Me got amulet here.
Not so fast! The reward...?
You not grab so fast! Me wants reward...
Text: 너무 빨리 가져가지 마! 나 보상 원해...

TextEng: Right. Time to kill you.
A key and some... lever? You better have a better reward that this!
Text: 열쇠랑 무슨... 레버? 이거보다 더 나은 보상이 있어야지!

TextEng: That works for me.
Uh-huh. You dies now.
Key and stick? You gives better reward... now!
Text: 열쇠랑 막대기? 더 좋은 보상 줘... 지금!

TextEng: Is okay with me.
You forgets it. Me go now.
I'll listen to nothing! Die, undead thing!
Text: 아무것도 안 들을 거야! 죽어, 언데드 놈!

TextEng: Me not listens! Undead dies!!
I've heard enough. Time to die!
Me hears enough! You dies!!
What's to stop me from taking it for myself?
What stops me from me taking it?
I'll go now.
Me go now.
I think I'll kill you and look for myself.
Me kills you and looks for it.
I've changed my mind. Time to die.
Me changes mind. You die now.
No, I haven't found it yet.
No, me not finds yet.
I never said I'd give it to you. Time to die!
Text: 너한테 준다고 한 적 없어. 이제 죽어!

TextEng: Me not givings it to you. You die now!
Text: 나 너한테 안 줘. 이제 죽어!
